{{primary sources|date=April 2017}} {{Infobox treaty | name = The Nairobi Convention | long_name = Convention for the Development, Protection, Management and Development of the Marine and Coastal Environment of the Western Indian Ocean | image = Nairobi Convention Logo.jpg | image_alt = image of the Official logo of the Convention | caption = Official logo of the Convention | type = Convention | context = [[:Category:Environmental treaties|Marine conservation]] | date_signed = {{Start date|1985|06|21}} | location_signed = [[Nairobi]], [[Kenya]] | date_sealed = | date_effective = {{Start date|1996|05|30}} | condition_effective = | date_expiry = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | mediators = <!-- format this as a bullet list --> | negotiators = <!-- format this as a bullet list --> | signatories = <!-- format this as a bullet list --> | parties = <!-- format this as a bullet list --> *{{flag|Comoros}} *{{flag|France}} *{{flag|Kenya}} *{{flag|Madagascar}} *{{flag|Mauritius}} *{{flag|Mozambique}} *{{flag|Seychelles}} *{{flag|Somalia}} *{{flag|Tanzania }} *{{flag| South Africa}}
